invited to resume their negotiations. 
  He pointed out the talks between Syria, Israel and the 
United 
States, despite their seriousness, are still far away from 
reaching an agreement among them. 
  "So it is necessary to make more endeavors and efforts in 
order to achieve this purpose," the foreign minister said. 

