<H3> <TI>   Qian Qichen Inspects Hubei Province </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Qian Qichen Inspects Hubei Province </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   OW2405130494 Beijing Central Television Program One Network 
in Mandarin 1100 GMT 23 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> OW2405130494 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing Central Television Program One Network 
in Mandarin 1100 GMT 23 May 94 </F>

<F P=105> Mandarin </F>


