remove the following functionaries on 26 and 27 April: 
  Wu Xiongwei (0702 7160 0251) was appointed vice chairman of 
the Hebei Provincial People's Government general office; Wang 
Defang (3769 1795 5364) was appointed vice chairman of the Hebei 
