was appointed deputy director of the Hebei Provincial 
Statistical Bureau; and Fei Jianjun (6316 1696 6874) was 
appointed adviser to the Hebei Provincial Statistical Bureau, 
and relieved of his post as director of the Hebei Provincial 
Statistical Bureau. 

